,"tid":2463443,"uid":3432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"巴打i know that feel<br />\n我都有甲亢 已經第2次復發食緊藥 但好彩既係冇去到眼突既情況 <br />\n我都唔想切左佢 想博下會唔會有朝一日停藥時唔會再復發<br />\n因為見都有唔少人切左就變埋甲減 都係死<br />\n<br />\n另外我都有睇緊婦科 細個一開始黎m時已經唔正常<br />\n係完全唔識停 搞到又貧血<br />\n睇過幾個醫生又話咩青春期係會亂hea9我 之後去到中五醫生有開d避孕丸調經 但一停藥就變左唔識黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿幾歲人都唔知正常黎m究竟會係點<br />\n<br />\n因為荷爾蒙咁亂 所以皮膚都差 搞到之前又要睇皮膚科<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企人完全冇呢d病痛 呀媽白白淨黎m都準 唔知點解我會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f5e50316c5bc0da3423060d45f4bd1ff7adde2","tid":2463443,"uid":44127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"929279dfbd1defd6a9371ca457f2207024079e5d","tid":2463443,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"400c04cc7529d22982ea54a59587f6fd9a684a9c","tid":2463443,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"肥定瘦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n不過啲人會覺得我肥<br />\n因為甲狀腺腫搞到條頸好撚腫，睇落會以為肥到好似有雙下巴咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0171edaea6fd7d804adca72493723825372587","tid":2463443,"uid":277252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"加油Ching 希望你快啲好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83066729db14c0925051891542773120c49ca930","tid":2463443,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"想問ching係咪中度肥胖嗰種？"},{"pid":"2ea6f774253f12caff06ac857ada56ca145e03f7","tid":2463443,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 